The STLinuxTV documentation is made of several parts:
	* STLinuxTV Implementation Report
	* LinuxTV customized documentation

STLinuxTV Implementation Report
===============================
This document describes the various devices/API provided by the STLinuxTV layer.
It does NOT intend to describe the API of each device precisely but instead of
that gives important information about each devices (ex: data format supported, type of buffer, buffer constraints etc)
It also give information about API changes between releases.

LinuxTV customized documentation
================================
This document is a customized version of the media API documentation found in
the vanilla Linux kernel source tree. ST specific extension are added.
